<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>What We Improved Recently | Apple Health Analyzer</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Simple timeline of recent improvements to our iOS and Mac app." />
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://applehealthdata.com/changelog.html" />
  <style>
    body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;max-width:860px;margin:36px auto;padding:0 18px;line-height:1.6;color:#111;background:#fff;}
    h1{margin:0 0 8px;font-size:2rem;}
    .sub{margin:0 0 20px;color:#555;}
    .timeline{position:relative;margin:24px 0 0;padding-left:26px;}
    .timeline:before{content:"";position:absolute;left:8px;top:0;bottom:0;width:2px;background:#e5e7eb;}
    .day{position:relative;margin:0 0 24px 0;}
    .day:before{content:"";position:absolute;left:-22px;top:8px;width:10px;height:10px;border-radius:50%;background:#111;}
    h2{font-size:1.05rem;margin:0 0 8px;color:#111;}
    ul{margin:0;padding-left:18px;}
    li{margin:8px 0;color:#222;}
    .meta{margin-top:26px;color:#666;font-size:.92rem;}
    .back{display:inline-block;margin-bottom:16px;color:#0b63ce;text-decoration:none;}
    .back:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
    .badge{display:inline-block;background:#f3f4f6;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:999px;font-size:.78rem;color:#444;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="back" href="/">← Back to home</a>
  <h1>Recent App Improvements</h1>
  <p class="sub">A plain-language timeline of what changed in our iOS and Mac app.</p>
  <span class="badge">Showing 16 updates since 2026-01-17</span>
  <div class="timeline">
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-02-14</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Integrated recent development updates into the main app branch.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-02-13</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Improved AI model choices so users can pick OpenAI, Claude, or Gemini more easily.</li>
        <li>Added support for smart ring health metrics in exports.</li>
        <li>Clarified that AI analysis is free when you use your own API key.</li>
        <li>Expanded internal quality checklist to make feature rollouts more reliable.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-02-12</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fixed a sleep tracking issue that could double-count sleep duration.</li>
        <li>Improved error messages so failed imports are easier to understand and fix.</li>
        <li>Improved large file handling so big exports load more reliably.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-02-08</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fixed chart labels on Mac so graphs are easier to read.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-02-05</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Integrated recent development updates into the main app branch.</li>
        <li>Added daily view summaries for quicker trend checks.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-02-01</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Improved first-time sync stability on iPhone and fixed a unit-related crash.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-01-31</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fix data export to include complete history by default.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-01-24</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Use HKStatisticsCollectionQuery for accurate daily step counts in exports.</li>
        <li>Add social sharing cards, ios companion qr code, and update app store links.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section class="day">
      <h2>2026-01-22</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fix fallback parsing and add mood results.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
  <p class="meta">This page focuses on product changes only (iOS + Mac app).</p>
</body>
</html>
